query:
SELECT 
  'Assignment Info' as info_type,
  pq.id as assignment_id,
  tq.questionnaireId as questionnaire_id_from_touchpoint
FROM partnerQuestionnaires pq
LEFT JOIN touchpointQuestionnaires tq ON pq.touchpointQuestionnaireId = tq.id
WHERE pq.accessCode = 'DDSETM9RNAHB'

UNION ALL

SELECT 
  'Question Count' as info_type,
  NULL as assignment_id,
  questionnaireId as questionnaire_id_from_touchpoint
FROM questions
GROUP BY questionnaireId
